</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【CES 2022】Razer Zephyr Pro 智能口罩，內置喇叭輸出音量達 60 分貝</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/06/razers-new-zephyr-pro-mask-has-the-voice-amp/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=razers-new-zephyr-pro-mask-has-the-voice-amp</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jan 2022 07:55:48 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[CES 2022]]></category><category><![CDATA[razer]]></category><category><![CDATA[Zephyr]]></category><category><![CDATA[Zephyr Pro]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1079896</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Razer 去年曾於 CES 2021 推出 Zephyr 智慧型口罩，其具備雙向防護的 N95 等級濾材強化 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Razer 去年曾於 CES 2021 推出 Zephyr 智慧型口罩，其具備雙向防護的 N95 等級濾材強化防疫，以及兩段速雙進氣風扇幫助空氣流通。時至今年的 CES 2022，Razer 推出了升級版本的 Zephyr Pro。口罩底部配備具語音放大功能的喇叭，可在一米範圍內以 60 分貝音量輸出聲音。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1079897" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture8-694x308.png" alt="" width="694" height="308" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture8-694x308.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture8-1280x568.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture8-768x341.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture8-1536x681.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture8.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">去年推出的 </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Razer Zephyr 因考慮到重量及電池續航力問題，因此未有安裝原先理想中的語音放大器。升級過後的 </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Zephyr Pro 則成功配備了語音放大功能，在口罩底部設有喇叭，透過按壓口罩上的按鍵以控制喇叭打開或關閉，喇叭開啟後能在一米範圍內以 60 分貝音量輸出聲音；</span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Zephyr Pro 亦</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">具備雙向防護的 N95 等級濾材及兩段速度雙進氣風扇的換氣腔，在過濾的空氣的同時保持其順暢流動，活動力較大或偏好更多空氣流通的使用者更可以透過多功能按鍵切換具備 2 個可調整高速模式 (4200/6200 RPM) 的風扇。</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">在外觀上，</span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Zephyr Pro 採用透明設計並搭配發光功能，使用者即使在黑暗中也可讓別人看到自身的臉部表情。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1079898" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/zephyr-pro-stay-safe-1-v2.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="350" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/zephyr-pro-stay-safe-1-v2.jpg 350w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/zephyr-pro-stay-safe-1-v2-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 350px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1079899" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/zephyr-pro-stay-safe-2.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="350" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/zephyr-pro-stay-safe-2.jpg 350w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/zephyr-pro-stay-safe-2-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 350px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1079900" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/zephyr-pro-stay-safe-3.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="350" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/zephyr-pro-stay-safe-3.jpg 350w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/zephyr-pro-stay-safe-3-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 350px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Zephyr Pro 和前身 </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Zephyr 均</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">保持相同的重量約 206.1 公克，多出的揚聲器重量則透過為底部口罩開孔作抵消。在空氣濾淨器打開的情況下，電池續航力約在 5 到 6 小時。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1079902" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture7-694x308.png" alt="" width="694" height="308" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture7-694x308.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture7-1280x568.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture7-768x341.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture7-1536x681.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Capture7.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：</span><a href="https://www.razer.com/hk-zh/gear-accessories/razer-zephyr-pro"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Razer</span></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
